WEBVTT

00:00.305 --> 00:02.289
<i>Previously on "Making History"...</i>

00:02.594 --> 00:04.664
1919 Chicago!

00:04.805 --> 00:07.006
- I know Al Capone!
- (glass shatters)

00:07.132 --> 00:09.117
I <i> am</i> Al Capone.

00:09.242 --> 00:11.492
- Let's just get this over with. Good-bye.
- CHRIS: No!

00:11.608 --> 00:13.645
The World Series is fixed.
The Chicago White Sox

00:13.679 --> 00:15.318
- are gonna throw it.
- DAN: And we're making a big bet.

00:15.343 --> 00:17.136
We can cut you in, and we
can all make a lot of money!

00:17.161 --> 00:19.004
Could we just have our bag back, please?

00:19.028 --> 00:20.161
Why don't we just wait and see

00:20.196 --> 00:24.180
how our little bet turns out first,
gentlemen, shall we?

00:25.132 --> 00:29.496
